UGH, I'm PISSED...apparently the tablet was a sSERIAL tablet, so it doesn't plug into my freggin laptop....okay! no problem, I'll go buy an adapter!

I drive over to fry's during rush hour btw, and realize that I don't have my freggin wallet, so okay, I'll just see if they have it and then leave it somewhere and come back. I find a 9prong male to 9 prong male and I'm satisfied and drive back to get my wallet. I drive back over there and purchased the item and drove back home. Then I pull the adapter out and stick it on the tablet and realize that my laptop's ISN'T A 9 PRONG, IT WAS RHE HD 15 PRONG ONE. SHIT. So I drive back and return what I bought for store credit and decided to do the SMART THING and ask a store associate about it. He finds me one that attaches as a usb, and I'll like PERFECT. I buy the item and leave AGAIN. I attach it together and YES it's been detected!

So I download the intuos2 driver (cuz vista sucks and doesnt believe in cds) and try to set it up. It doesn't work, then pen and mouse DON'T WORK, so I download the other version, same result, and then I download the last version and read the inscription and it says that it's for serial tablet and ADAPTERS HAVE UNEXPECTED RESULTS, so BASICALLY, it DOENS'T WORK EVER UNLESS YOU HAVE AN OLD ASS COMPUTER!

okay..FINE! I'll use my MOM's computer cuz it has the serial plug, so I plug it in and set it up, it works! yaaaay! Not for long...

I open photoshop and try to open a picture to start photoshopping. ERROR, your scratch disks are full! and I'm like SHIT WTF. I mean I used to have this problem ALL the time cuz I like to use up all my space on C:/ and then I just transfer and burn stuff off when that happens. NO PROBLEM, I'll just transfer files or delete them. I open My Computer and there's a bunch of drives, each have about 8 gig and I check all of the drives to see how much free space each one has and all of them are free except C:/ which has like 24 MB left...- -

so I open that drive and check out what I can delete. ALL OF THEM ARE FREGGIN PROGRAM FILES, I can't delete any of them cuz I either don't know if they're important and 2 most of them really didn't take up that much space, like 100 MB-ish or less. I argue with my uncle about what the hell is going on and he tells me that all chinese windows softwares work like this, they take ur hdd and split the space into like 3-4 drives in which C:/ is for XP and program files.

While we are having trouble communicating (cuz of the language), I try to explain to him that C:/ ran out of space and I can't open any programs cuz there's probably not enough RAM (which I cant figure out how much there is cuz the properties wont show me). His solution is to uninstall all the programs not needed and reinstall them later when I'm done. That's utter nonsense, who wants to spend hours resetting up all the programs, I didn't even like doing them in the first place!

I also tried asking him if we could add space or transfer space around, or when we set up windows, can we customize how many gig we want in each drive. He either has no idea or it's a no. The only solution I can think up is 1). Set AMERICAN XP back on 2). Get a bigger internal and reset up the chinese one 3). Maybe see if my theories would work to customize the space values.  Problem with 1 is that my mom needs chinese, if I set up the english one, she'll freak and ask me to fix everything and make stuff chinese. Problem with 2 is I don't understand chinese so my uncle would have to do it, which will probably make him mad to change my mom's windows AGAIN. Problem with 3 is that it's just a theory and it's most likely NOT likely.

I'm really in angst about this stupid tablet and I'm stuck with solutions...I'm outta time to get a new tablet or change it or anything. I don't have any other computers to use except maybe my friend's but I only really do things at night and I think there's only one person's computer I can use if it even has the 9 prong serial port.

My solutions with the tablet is 1). resell it on ebay and find a new one 2). try to get a return and pay for the shipping and find a new one 3). see if the computers in savannah will have the 9 prong serial port and plug I can use with it (cuz it needs electricity....- -)

god it's huge...- - It's bigger than my laptop flat and my laptop isnt one of the small ones either..


Another thing with the stupid chinese xp is that I CANT SCAN ANYTHING CUZ THE SCRATCH DISKS ARE FREGGIN FULL. I can't even scan 300 dpi! I was in luck to even get 200DPI. FUCK. I wanted to try for 2400 dpi too. I tried setting the scanner onto my laptop but for SOME ODD REASON, there's an error, so it can't be used....stupid vista...I hate vista, I hate serial ports, I hate CHINESE XP and it's REALLY STUPID METHOD OF MEMORY. I mean seriously?! What IF you run out of space like me! THEN WHAT DO YOU DO FUCKTARDS?! I'm so freggin pissed about this. - -


I've wasted like 10 hours and I still have shit to do on my shitty laptop where the wireless mouse doesnt work properly b/c it keeps disconnecting for some reason and the touchpad acts up ALL the time. CAN'T EVEN SCAN, which I need a high quality picture SHIT.

I thought maybe if the tablet didn't work, I could just use the my old tablet and the new pen, but I guess it's that intuos2 came before the graphire3 so it doesnt work...Does anybody know if a newer pen works on an older tablet?
http://shiawase-chan.livejournal.com/1611.html

I'm excited! I just won an auction for a really big tablet for like $215! It's like a 12x18 intuos2 tablet.

At first I was worried that intuos2 would be way worse than intuos3 but then I read it's just the scrolly things that are different and I guess a different feel, so I'm cool now, cuz I hated the scroll thing. I'd look away for a second and the picture is suddenly bigger and I'm like WTF and I was like ohh..I just touched the scroll thing (I borrowed this from Sarah btw).

So, I was like, "WHAT IF I GOT RIPPED OFF??!!" It used to happen a lot. I guess it's cuz no one really tried to hard to win at the end so it made me worry O_o I think I bought one bigger than Sarah's...hopefully I can get used to it (I think I'd have to use a lot of exaggerated movements....gahhhhh





I GOT RID OF FLORAL WHITE. I told you Sarah already, so I can post here what new markers I bought and traded illegally - -;;; It was 30% off from $5.99 so about $4 a marker XD

I got mallow (FInally have purple XD), chrome orange (got my orange yay!!) , fruit pink, powder pink, skin white (I was running out of milky white so I panicked and bought a lot okay?), warm gray no 5 (needed a warm gray for white shadow), garnet (just liked it), and burnt umber (need a darker brown even tho I havent used it yet, lol). I found the special black and cool gray 3 I borrowed from Farren that I forgot to give back - -;;;

I still want amethyst, lapis lazuli, process blue (wanna trade with my tahitian blue lol),  frost blue/new blue, Peacock blue? DAMNIT TOO MANY BLUES! Maybe moss? Right now I have 20 markers, so I SHOULD limit my collection to 24....but I might get more if hobby lobby actually adds to its collection (they have one of the 36 sets or something cuz the colors are the same)

I finished my first copic picture, and I'm almost done with the Spade Magician, but I still have to finish the cards and sceptre, then I need to edit and get them printed so I can sell it at onicon in a FREGGIN WEEK NOOOOOO!!!! CRAP MUFFINS!!



The pink is my first Copic project, the magician is my second, the one I have on dA is the third, red lolita is fourth, and I'm working on the fifth for my manga.


I now figured out that my disciple had copic markers! I'm asking her to bring them to Oni-Con so I can do copic commissions like everyone else. Still need to figure out the prices...I might copy ecthelian's prices but a little cheaper maybe? Anyone know any other people who do copic commissions with set prices, cuz I wanna figure out what's a good price for people, but will still be enough for the effort i put in O-o I'm practicing with the markers right now with my manga characters and the lolita fashion ^___^

ecthelian's prices are bust up ($45), Waist up ($65), Full Body ($80+) and additional characters are $40-$60 + each? Are these prices reasonable for me? I don't wanna be too cheap but I do want business...O___O

Okay, I'm gonna blog about my life in SCAD so I don't have to explain to a thousand people at different times about the same thing over and over again. Yay! Ranting time!

So when my dad and I drove all the way to Savannah (stopping at Atlanta first) for like 3 days, I was finally free from his lecturing. Instead I had to listen to SCAD lecture for like another week. At first they had good speakers, but they got progressively more boring as time led on...

I'm not even going to blog about how much my meal plan has made me suffer.....$1260 for a bunch of hateful workers who hate their jobs...some of them are alright...grrr..... biggest waste of money ever...

     

These are the dorms and the picture on the right is our hall's mascot. We got green ranger XD



 
I got these at the Art Trade Show. They were $60 for 12 markers. TT-TT crying wallet >< I'm thinking these will be the only colors I'll really need other than purple, but I'll buy 12 more and call it safe. XD  The colors are Light Pink, Shock Pink, Lipstick Red, Golden Yellow, Canary Yellow, Salad, Lettuce Green, Tahitian Blue (I wanted Process Blue TT_TT), Milky White, Sepia, Special Black, Colorless Blender, and the color I'll never use...Floral White (It was a present from Sarah cuz she somehow accidently bought like 3 of them).


 
This is Sarah, I took a close up picture...>_>


 

So as we walk down "rape alley", we can always see this grafitti on the wall, really brightens your day. I had to change the color so it was more readable. O_O In another path, there's a security pole for emergencies. So, push this button for help if you are getting raped.



This is the security car, sometimes it parks in student spaces when it has it's own personal space. - - *angry face*



    

I found a car with the front license plate labeled as wasaabi, lol. It was manufactured by SAAB or something. Someone on campus rides a pink vespa on campus apparently, and I saw a bike with Aluminum foil on the wheels ( I don't know it that's normal?).



Since I started living with my roommate, I discovered the joys of Jello XD




We had a chess game with all the pirates. We were supposed to have the cosplay club against the pirates, but cosplay club didn't get a permission form signed or something? Which I can't understand why we just do i for fun anyway? So it was like 16 pirates and 3 cosplayers? We switched it to red vs blue. Isn't the captain's outfit awesome? I think his mom made it for him for prom. I want a hat like that...




I accidentally took this when I trying to take a picture of the building in the dark with the camera setting on "P". Then my roommate and I started playing around with it and took pictures of random lights like christmas lights and the moon to make cool designs XD This one is still my favorite.





Mellow Mushroom! :D Such a cute name ^_^. They apparently have really good pizza there, but I haven't tried it yet >< There's enough pizza with the stupid meal plan....- -




We went on a field trip to an art hall and they gave us Beebleheads. It's some kinda alliance lol. It's so cute X3!





 
If you can't read that, it says " Your a fucking idiot who cant park suck a dick you dumb bitch." I don't know why they bothered to put the period, the grammar was so bad already....so what had happened was we were late to class so my roommate parked perpendicularly too close to another car, so they were kinda trapped. When we came back from class we found a cup from the sub shop in half on the car and this receipt next to it. My roommate though the "park" looked like "porn", which after I looked at it again, I couldn't tell how it resembled park at all. Who's really the idiot on this one?

   

Gas priced went down and I decided to buy a gas tank to buy extra gas for my tank in case it went back up, which was stupid. Apparently I put the cap on wrong and with my semi-drifting turns, the gas spilled in my trunk, which took a while for me to discover. After I discovered it, I emptied the rest of the gas into the gas tank of my car. I left the windows open to air out the smell, but it never went away. I checked the back later and found my air compressor glued to the carpet. The gas eroded the plastic on the compressor so it took me like half an hour to peel the compressor off the carpet. I went back to my room reeking of gasoline.

A few days later, I was sick of the smell and it hit me. The rest of the gas leaked through the carpet and is probably now in a puddle at the bottom of the trunk with the wheel. I lift the carpet and my suspicions were right (my blonde moments....- - ). I was like shit shit shit! So I went to Walmart to get it fixed and they said I should go to the car wash. I sat in the cold for like 2 hours waiting for them to finish. It was cheaper than I expected, so I was happy. Good thing I didn't have to drive two days with the sickening smell. It still kinda smells right now though.....- -

Don't judge me....>____<




This really bothers me why there's a hole in the parking lot....It leads to never never land.

Okay, so this morning, I decided to bake off those onigiri and save myself from laziness. So I stuck them in the little oven so I can save some energy. Everything should have been right. 275 degrees in 15 minutes, right?



So then after the timer goes off, I go check the onigiri to take them out.

and....


BAM! Whaaat the HELL is THAT?! I can understand a little burnt corners and darkened white clay, but...WHAT THE HELL HAPPENED!!1??

so if anyone wants to buy that one, I'll give it to you for a $1 (for shipping). I dun even care about the money, I just want someone else to witness the monstrosity I have created....O______O Maybe it's cuz I didnt properly preheat the oven???




These were waiting to be baked back at my dorm. Looks tasty XD

It kept moving around so I couldnt get a decent picture until I brought it inside. No...I don't know the gender. >_>
